overview: Here, Nora Nord plays, among other things, the role of a dirty cop. She does it convincingly. Nora, wearing a leather cap, loaded puffer and handcuffs, would probably make anyone dream of being caught. And she finds completely different ways to use the baton than to hit people in the head with. Tina is very happy with her gardener and Tess has a busy day at the doctor.
title: Oops!... Nu Gick Det Igen
